# Agent autonomy — hub Playwright, no vision, no Copilot

## Browser automation (hub WSL)

- **Use Playwright DOM** — `get_by_text`, locators, network sniff. Never Gemini screenshot clicking.
- **Never open Microsoft Copilot** on the hub desktop — use Edge headless on WSL only.
- **Profiles:** `momentum_academy/` (course), `discord/` (Discord web), `kalodata/` (scout).
- **Credentials:** `data/agent_credentials.env` on hub (gitignored) — not in repo.

## Commands (cloud → hub)

```bash
bash scripts/hub_course_deep_crawl.sh      # full Momentum crawl
bash scripts/hub_discord_crawl.sh          # Discord read-only
bash scripts/hub_adb_windows.sh            # phone on USB (Windows adb)
python3 -m shorts_bot.owner_ping "message" # ping owner when blocked
```

## When owner is away

- Crawl course + Discord, parse weekly drop, update scout rules from inbox.
- Do **not** post, send Discord messages, or buy services.
- Log blockers to inbox + owner_ping if SMTP/Slack configured.

